The http://cityofdavis.org/media/ City Government Channel (Comcast Media Channel 16), is operated as a public service by the Parks & Community Services Department for the citizens of Davis. The channel carries live and tape delayed coverage of City Council and Planning Commission meetings, coverage of meetings of other City commissions and committees, special events of public interest, and information on City services and programs.

There is also http://media.city.davis.ca.us:554/ramgen/encoder/live.rm live streaming video, but you must install software from http://www.real.com/ Real to use it. wiki:WikiPedia:Realvideo Realvideo is a wiki:WikiPedia:Proprietary proprietary format.

